# Design Tokens Standards

## Token Structure

The Kueski Design System uses a comprehensive token system located in `/packages/react/src/styles/tokens/`:

### Token Categories

- **Colors** (`colors.css`): Brand, semantic, and utility colors
- **Spacing** (`spacings.css`): Consistent spacing scale
- **Typography** (`font-sizes.css`, `font-weights.css`, `line-heights.css`): Text sizing and weights
- **Radius** (`radius.css`): Border radius values
- **Shadows** (`colors.css`): Elevation and shadow tokens
- **Gradients** (`gradients.css`): Linear gradient definitions

## Color Tokens

### Brand Colors

```css
--color-background-brand: #0069f1;
--color-background-brand-subtle: #e7f3ff;
--color-stroke-brand: #0069f1;
```

### Semantic Colors

```css
--color-background-danger: #d82938;
--color-background-success: #008246;
--color-background-warning: #ab5d00;
--color-background-upsell: #6e5be6;
```

### Text Colors

```css
--color-text-and-icons-primary: #141c22;
--color-text-and-icons-secondary: #384550;
--color-text-and-icons-always-white: #ffffff;
```

### Usage in Components

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using color tokens
'bg-background-brand text-text-and-icons-always-white';
'bg-background-danger text-text-and-icons-always-white';
'text-text-and-icons-primary';

// ❌ Wrong - hardcoded colors
'bg-blue-500 text-white';
'bg-red-500 text-white';
'text-gray-900';
```

## Spacing Tokens

### Spacing Scale

```css
--spacing-x1: 0.25rem; /* 4px */
--spacing-x2: 0.5rem; /* 8px */
--spacing-x3: 0.75rem; /* 12px */
--spacing-x4: 1rem; /* 16px */
--spacing-x5: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
--spacing-x6: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
--spacing-x7: 1.75rem; /* 28px */
--spacing-x8: 2rem; /* 32px */
```

### Usage in Components

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using spacing tokens
'px-x4 py-x3'; // 16px horizontal, 12px vertical
'mx-x2 my-x1'; // 8px horizontal, 4px vertical
'gap-x3'; // 12px gap

// ❌ Wrong - hardcoded spacing
'px-4 py-3'; // Use px-x4 py-x3 instead
'mx-2 my-1'; // Use mx-x2 my-x1 instead
'gap-3'; // Use gap-x3 instead
```

## Typography Tokens

### Font Sizes

```css
--text-headline-1: 2rem; /* 32px */
--text-headline-2: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
--text-headline-3: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
--text-body-1: 1rem; /* 16px */
--text-body-2: 0.875rem; /* 14px */
--text-meta: 0.75rem; /* 12px */
--text-mini: 0.6875rem; /* 11px */
--text-amount: 4rem; /* 64px */
```

### Typography Utilities

Use predefined typography utilities from `/packages/react/src/styles/utility/typography.css`:

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using typography utilities
'typo-headline-1'; // Headline 1 with proper font features
'typo-headline-2'; // Headline 2 with proper font features
'typo-headline-3'; // Headline 3 with proper font features
'typo-body-1'; // Body 1 text
'typo-body-2'; // Body 2 text
'typo-body-2-emphasized'; // Body 2 with emphasis
'typo-meta'; // Meta text
'typo-amount'; // Amount/currency text

// ❌ Wrong - manual typography
'text-2xl font-bold'; // Use typo-headline-1 instead
'text-xl font-semibold'; // Use typo-headline-2 instead
'text-lg font-medium'; // Use typo-headline-3 instead
'text-base'; // Use typo-body-1 instead
'text-sm font-medium'; // Use typo-body-2-emphasized instead
```

## Radius Tokens

### Border Radius Scale

```css
--radius-x1: 0.25rem; /* 4px */
--radius-x2: 0.5rem; /* 8px */
--radius-x3: 0.75rem; /* 12px */
--radius-x4: 1rem; /* 16px */
--radius-x5: 1.25rem; /* 20px */
--radius-x6: 1.5rem; /* 24px */
```

### Usage in Components

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using radius tokens
'rounded-x2'; // 8px border radius
'rounded-x4'; // 16px border radius
'rounded-t-x2'; // 8px top border radius

// ❌ Wrong - hardcoded radius
'rounded-md'; // Use rounded-x2 instead
'rounded-lg'; // Use rounded-x4 instead
'rounded-t-md'; // Use rounded-t-x2 instead
```

## Shadow Tokens

### Shadow Scale

```css
--color-shadows-s3: #00000008; /* Very light shadow */
--color-shadows-s5: #0000000d; /* Light shadow */
--color-shadows-s6: #0000000f; /* Subtle shadow */
--color-shadows-s8: #00000014; /* Medium shadow */
--color-shadows-s10: #0000001a; /* Strong shadow */
--color-shadows-s15: #00000026; /* Very strong shadow */
--color-shadows-s20: #00000033; /* Maximum shadow */
```

### Usage in Components

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using shadow tokens
'shadow-s3'; // Very light shadow
'shadow-s8'; // Medium shadow
'shadow-s15'; // Strong shadow

// ❌ Wrong - hardcoded shadows
'shadow-sm'; // Use shadow-s3 instead
'shadow-md'; // Use shadow-s8 instead
'shadow-lg'; // Use shadow-s15 instead
```

## Gradient Tokens

### Linear Gradients

```css
--gradient-brand: linear-gradient(135deg, #0069f1 0%, #0056cc 100%);
--gradient-destructive: linear-gradient(135deg, #d82938 0%, #b71c1c 100%);
--gradient-success: linear-gradient(135deg, #008246 0%, #006633 100%);
```

### Usage in Components

```typescript
// ✅ Correct - using gradient tokens
'bg-linear-brand'; // Brand gradient
'bg-linear-destructive'; // Destructive gradient
'bg-linear-success'; // Success gradient

// ❌ Wrong - hardcoded gradients
'bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600';
```

## Component Implementation

### CVA with Design Tokens

```typescript
import { cva } from 'class-variance-authority';

export const buttonVariants = cva(
  // Base styles using design tokens
  [
    'typo-body-2-emphasized whitespace-nowrap rounded-x2',
    'flex items-center justify-center w-fit',
    'disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:cursor-not-allowed',
    'relative overflow-hidden focus-visible:!outline-[2px] focus-visible:!outline-offset-2 focus-visible:!outline-stroke-brand',
  ],
  {
    variants: {
      $variant: {
        primary: [
          'bg-background-brand !text-text-and-icons-always-white',
          'border-background-brand',
          'hover:bg-linear-brand active:bg-linear-pressed-brand focus-visible:bg-linear-brand',
        ],
        secondary: [
          'bg-background-secondary text-text-and-icons-primary',
          'border-stroke-secondary',
          'hover:bg-background-tertiary active:bg-background-tertiary',
        ],
      },
      $size: {
        sm: 'px-x3 py-x2 text-typo-body-3 min-h-[32px]',
        md: 'px-x4 py-x3 text-typo-body-2 min-h-[40px]',
        lg: 'px-x6 py-x4 text-typo-body-1 min-h-[48px]',
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: {
      $variant: 'primary',
      $size: 'md',
    },
  },
);
```

## Best Practices

### 1. Always Use Tokens

```typescript
// ✅ Good - consistent with design system
'bg-background-brand text-text-and-icons-always-white px-x4 py-x3 rounded-x2';

// ❌ Bad - inconsistent with design system
'bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-md';
```

### 2. Use Typography Utilities

```typescript
// ✅ Good - using typography utilities
'typo-headline-1 text-text-and-icons-primary';

// ❌ Bad - manual typography
'text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900';
```

### 3. Consistent Spacing

```typescript
// ✅ Good - using spacing tokens
'p-x4 m-x2 gap-x3';

// ❌ Bad - inconsistent spacing
'p-4 m-2 gap-3';
```

### 4. Semantic Colors

```typescript
// ✅ Good - using semantic colors
'bg-background-danger text-text-and-icons-always-white';

// ❌ Bad - using generic colors
'bg-red-500 text-white';
```

## Token Maintenance

- **Never modify tokens directly** - use the design system tools
- **Always use the latest tokens** - keep tokens updated
- **Test token changes** - ensure consistency across components
- **Document token usage** - maintain clear documentation
